                Matta Cato<lb break="no" n="2"/>nis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LXX<lb break="no" n="3"/>V <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <surplus>YI</surplus> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>matri <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Blattförmige Hederae als Wortrenner in Z. 1-3. Oberhalb der Inschrift in Rechtecknische sitzende weibliche Figur in einheimischer Tracht. (B): Diebold: Z. 3/4: yi(nta) s(ita) e(st) fili(us) / matri p(osuit).</p>
